{
  "texts": [
    "Through questionnaires and assessments, Wealthfront determines optimal asset allocation, including stocks, stock options, debt, and real estate, thereby maximizing investment returns through automated management services.The automated investment management process at Wealthfront follows five steps:1.",
    "Assessment of the current investment environment to determine the ideal asset class.2.",
    "Selection of low-cost ETFs representing each asset class.3.",
    "Evaluation of risk tolerance to create a suitable investment portfolio.4.",
    "Application of modern investment portfolio theory (MPT) to spread risk."
  ]
}